      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and the interior is still smelling fresh. It\u2019s been pampered and garage-kept its whole life. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the dealership price tag, you've found it! Drop me a message and come see it for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
