    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine example of the FD3S RX-7, featuring the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. This vehicle exhibits exceptional mechanical integrity, with the vacuum lines recently replaced and the cooling system upgraded for thermal management. The chassis remains rigid, supported by original double-wishbone suspension components and factory-spec bushings. The five-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, delivering power through a Torsen limited-slip differential. The exterior retains its original high-gloss finish, while the interior shows no signs of sun damage or bolster wear. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning rotary purist.",
