    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since the day it was driven off the lot. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like luster without a single swirl mark, rock chip, or blemish. Inside, the cabin remains in an absolute pristine state; the premium leather upholstery still retains its factory-fresh scent and shows zero signs of wear, bolsters are firm, and the carpets are spotless. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity surround sound system to the intuitive navigation, functions exactly as it did on day one. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive log of every scheduled maintenance interval. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never been exposed to rain or snow. Included with the sale are all original keys, the complete owner\u2019s manual set, and a meticulously organized service history folder. For the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that is truly indistinguishable from new, this example stands alone.",
